node.text:
Our Recap video of DS Luxury representing the Chicago Supercar Scene at The Formula 1 Chicago Festival! 🏎 We brought out our Lamborghini Aventador S and Ferrari 488 Spider for people to take pictures and watch rip up the @f1 track set on Museum Campus Drive right outside of Soldier Field! What an amazing experience 🙌🏼💎🏁
🎥: @capturedbyankit
